{"tid":2080443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本首次有地方議會立例，禁止民眾走路時看手提電話","createTime":"2020-06-26T12:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T12:51:10.000Z","uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b81316ce6821ff6de6d710178ae8b7ea9bf986d6","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】日本首次有地方議會立例，禁止民眾走路時看手機。<br />\n神奈川縣大和市議會通過條例，下月起、民眾在公共場所，包括街道和公園等，如果想使用手機，必須在不會妨礙他人通行下站立使用，但未有訂明罰則。市政府年初研究發現，當地一成二行人都會一邊走路，一邊低頭看手機，為了減少相關行為引發的意外，市政府本月初向市議會提交相關條例草案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hs1ifCp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhs1ifCp.jpg&h=dea73d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港都應該咁做<br />\n太多自私友一路行一路㩒電話阻住其他人"},{"pid":"4f6d21c7586b41d10ad1f1965058eea7afc70d10","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc943dd5523e9644c550386813a39a46ae24cb7a","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8ac991967adc32c8ec7d0f1c64a5abe40db8259","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"14d8a31f4771fdba6ad020e28bf0c941760269c8","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0f032ac2eeaa723cec19901ebb5b57c681f06fb5","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe9e966a50e93d925e0a25c162d12de6e2c129b0","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a052976fc22bb598ca1a66f48895665011b081c7","tid":2080443,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40b494